<font color=#FFFF00>Kepala, ingat, 'kan?</font>

150
00:08:19,460 --> 00:08:22,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Segala insiden buruk biasanya menimpa Mu Yeong Sunbae.</font>

151
00:08:23,530 --> 00:08:28,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengerti.
Nam Kang Myung memiliki kemungkinan datang lewat sini juga.</font>

152
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kalian juga harus berhati-hati.</font>

153
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:34,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin akan terjadi adu tembak juga, jadi--</font>

154
00:08:34,010 --> 00:08:36,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Adu tembak apa?
Berhentilah bicara omong kosong, pergi saja.</font>

155
00:08:37,150 --> 00:08:38,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat masuk ke mobil itu.</font>

156
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:39,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian bawa kartu kredit perusahaan?</font>

157
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:41,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai jumpa.</font>

158
00:08:43,950 --> 00:08:45,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

159
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:49,530
<font color=#FFFF00>(Lebih baik bila kau tidak ke Pelabuhan Gung Pyung.)</font>

160
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:53,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Entahlah.</font>

161
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa saja ini jebakan,</font>

162
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,070
<font color=#FFFF00>atau mungkin...</font>

163
00:08:59,230 --> 00:09:00,800
<font color=#FFFF00>...kesempatan terakhir kita.</font>

164
00:09:02,870 --> 00:09:05,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Pikirkan sekali lagi. Kau yakin ingin pergi ke sana?</font>

165
00:09:05,610 --> 00:09:08,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Ingat saat Jurnalis Lee menyuruhku berhenti?</font>

166
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:12,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau berpikir tujuanku bukanlah mengoreksi kesalahan yang ada,
melainkan balas dendam.</font>

167
00:09:12,980 --> 00:09:13,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, itu--</font>

168
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:17,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi, aku terus memikirkannya.</font>

169
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:20,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Bertanya-tanya, haruskah aku menyerah?</font>

